    "Name": "Dragoon",
    "Details": "Designed as a short-ranged fighter, the -02 is armed with a single ER PPC, the remaining weapons space is filled by five medium lasers, a small pulse laser, and an AC/20. At the price of dropping its jump jets, the 'Mech's engine has been upgraded to an XL 350 to allow the 'Mech to close in quicker than the original model.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Modular Weapons</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.1</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Upper, Right Upper</color>",
